{"type":"text","timestamp":1782884066679,"sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","part":{"id":"prt_f1c2be2ee001UlKKtkM0pvF4S2","messageID":"msg_f1c2b85d40012cFpCwcqdS7G3R","sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","type":"text","text":"I’ll run this as the requested detached lineage, with writes confined to the provided `research/lineages/gpt` directory and reads limited to the skill contract plus packet/tooling evidence needed for the research loop.","time":{"start":1782884066030,"end":1782884066676},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_087c44870785d4b3016a44a6e2059c81919d58965f209381c0","phase":"commentary"}}}}
