{"type":"text","timestamp":1782884289891,"sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","part":{"id":"prt_f1c2f4cf5001V9LzBUQ6GUXTNJ","messageID":"msg_f1c2f2df4001ZsGPCX1wMFUkA8","sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","type":"text","text":"Iteration 1 found a high-confidence drift pattern: the parent map says top-level phases 002-007 are Complete, but several phase-parent maps still show their children as Draft while child metadata reports Complete.","time":{"start":1782884289781,"end":1782884289889},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08960f502441f910016a44a7c1c7d48191ac73348f0ac08266","phase":"commentary"}}}}
