 worked: Direct phase-map reads quickly confirmed a packet-wide drift class.\n+- What failed: A broad grep produced too many matches to enumerate all stale continuity fields in one pass.\n+- Ruled out: Treating 008 as entirely stale is outdated; it has at least some repaired continuity/key-file evidence now.\n+\n+## Recommended Next Focus\n+\n+Audit stale continuity frontmatter, scaffold docs, and empty complete-status plan/task shells.\n","additions":44,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/deep-research-state.jsonl","relativePath":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/deep-research-state.jsonl","type":"update","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/deep-research-state.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/deep-research-state.jsonl\n@@ -1,1 +1,2 @@\n {\"type\":\"config\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"loopType\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt-1782884040803-9tnd8n\",\"parentSessionId\":\"fanout-gpt-1782884040803-9tnd8n\",\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"generation\":1,\"topic\":\"Find upgrade, fix, and expansion recommendations to perfect the deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved packet across all 8 phases and its review tooling.\",\"maxIterations\":35,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.01,\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"executor\":\"cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-i