{"type":"text","timestamp":1782885284985,"sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","part":{"id":"prt_f1c3e3ba0001Xof3z7G93bKKVf","messageID":"msg_f1c3dfa4a001uDKTR9pLtP25Ev","sessionID":"ses_0e3d47d8bffeJ9bmuc4AVIwhXC","type":"text","text":"Convergence has not legally triggered yet because the last evidence iterations still add substantial novelty. I’m doing final targeted gap sweeps; if they produce no new findings, I’ll record no-new-information iterations until the `0.01` threshold can legally stop.","time":{"start":1782885268384,"end":1782885284984},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f233a6e23ea319b016a44ab9458808191ab85da8350c7acb1","phase":"commentary"}}}}
